{"tid":805727,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"3女搭滴滴遭性騷擾　司機：用條脷搞到妳哋嘰呱叫","createTime":"2018-09-04T05:23:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T06:50:38.000Z","uid":39464,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f82d9b1bb02a02aab156ef9af126c09e19c5c611","tid":805727,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T05:23:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20180904/photo/bkn-20180904053642108-0904_00952_001_01p.jpg?20180904121341\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20180904%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180904053642108-0904_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20180904121341&h=a89dbbaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n浙江溫州女乘客被滴滴司機姦殺後，滴滴的醜聞愈揭愈多。廣西南寧3名女生近日亦向媒體爆料，稱上月底乘搭滴滴順風車時，被司機不斷性騷擾，對方還聲言要將3人帶到僻靜處，要把她們「弄得嘰呱叫」。所幸她們及時下車，才避過一劫。 <br />\n<br />\n當事人劉女士憶述，上周日（8月26日）晚上9時許，她在南寧三塘的機動車考試點參加完的考試後，與其她兩名女學員一起，通過滴滴叫到了一輛車牌號為「桂AT6530」的順風車，打算搭去民族廣場附近。開車的是一名年約40歲的男司機，她們為安全起見，上車時決定一起坐在後排。<br />\n<br />\n惟開車不久，司機就開始講起溫州女乘客被姦殺一案，「我們都說那個事情真的好可怕，我們都不敢搭滴滴順風車了。然後司機說，等下我就把妳們拉到哪裡哪裡，就說那種話」。劉女士稱，她們起初以為司機在開玩笑，但對方竟愈說愈過分。 <br />\n<br />\n司機不斷向劉女士等人說些污穢不堪的言語，如「溫州那個司機一搞一，我就一搞三」、「一個舌頭就能把妳們三個搞得嘰呱叫」，令劉女士等人非常害怕，未到目的地即要求下車。涉事司機所屬於中鹿出租汽車公司周日（9月2日）表示會進行調查，若事件屬實將對司機作批評教育。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20180904/bkn-20180904053642108-0904_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20180904%2Fbkn-20180904053642108-0904_00952_001.html&d=AE7adLJ16%2Bv8t4P6ZbmGqmowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=fe3f8f0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20180904/bkn-20180904053642108-0904_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9ec8526c47d616986d4b2c4a6a1f53b287542957","tid":805727,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T05:33:22.000Z","msg":"咁都係批評下就算"},{"pid":"ac402e01f60a6171c9813acac76e25ecdb8fb1bc","tid":805727,"uid":18587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T05:43:02.000Z","msg":"滴滴都叫有機搵到司機，如果真係坐的士......真係被人溶左都唔會有人知，假車假牌假證"},{"pid":"1b7b92ab05c646c65bea8978a67fa2140bac79a4","tid":805727,"uid":184312,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T05:44:01.000Z","msg":"美國uber都一樣可能會發生 唔好抹黑我國"},{"pid":"622e17fafbe6026c3b8798f7b9ddae84c5399760","tid":805727,"uid":42367,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1b7b92ab05c646c65bea8978a67fa2140bac79a4","tid":805727,"uid":184312,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T05:44:01.000Z","msg":"美國uber都一樣可能會發生 唔好抹黑我國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T05:46:16.000Z","msg":"岩牙，呢個世界一定有好人壞人<br />\n<br />\n阿媽係女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e39b2ef9d109dc3a2f056b4be29881fffcc62fe","tid":805727,"uid":15211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T05:59:51.000Z","msg":"涉事司機所屬於中鹿出租汽車公司周日（9月2日）表示會進行調查，若事件屬實將對司機作批評教育。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d71360185c5c3bc436a5bd06e12a916b83bae4e","tid":805727,"uid":78165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T06:50:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}